public class TestBehavior
extends epfl.lia.logist.agent.behavior.Behavior

Behavior class of the test agent This class represents a behavior that is shared for all signals addressed to this agent. It handles almost all signals that should be handled by the reactive agent, and throws an exception for signals it doesn't understand.
